Proloque
»CL9:--------------------------------------
»CL7:Hello dear »CL8:Eurochart» readers.. For the
5th (or 6th ? I lost count :) I am
supporting The Official Eurohart in a
row. A pretty nice achievement if I
may say so.. This time again a Magical
Moments corner as in the previous two
issues, I hope you like them as much I
liked writing them filling up some
gaps in my spair time :) I am
supporting this legendary charts
magazine for as long as I can remember
I hope you will do the same for the
next issue goddamnit!! :) By the way,
Assembly has gone by again, and some
nice releases have merged from this
party. The most terrible news what
party's is concerned is that there
will not be an IntelOutside party in
Poland. What used to be a good source
for some (or alot) releases from
Polish groups. Maybe other party's
this year will make up for this ?







»CL8:The Summer of 1999..
