By the way did you all know Oktober is
a good month to go on holiday to Spain
for a week ? :)








»CL8:A Happy Amiga Scenish 1999
»CL9:»SML:--------------------------------------
»CL7:The scene just lives on. Who cares how
the past looked like ? I certainly
don't.. But isn't the Official
Eurochart for this goal and/or need ?
:) The Summer is almost over, and
AGAIN (yes I am still not getting
tired of writing this every year) we
are heading to the last part of the
year, where the whole scene will enjoy
The Party. Can we get some great
compo's finally atleast this year
overthere ? Get working Scene!

The next Magical Moments will soon be
finished. This because my great group
mate Darkus joined up, and we will try
to make the new Magical Moments even
better. Atleast we have a great
article from Majic Mushroom, who
interviewed a legendary coder from the
real OLD days.. But wait and see in
the next Magcial Moments corner.. Any
magazine out there who wants it ??


