personality ? To be known you have to
have a group of people to establish
your name in. Get voting! Enough votes
ensure the continuation of the Offical
Eurochart! Btw download issue 19
somewhere to see an old photo of me in
the Gallery :) (Taken Warsawa/Poland
in 1994 :)

